flowchart TD
    A["POST /api/internal-data/retrieve\nfile: src/backend/routers/internal_data.py\nfunction: retrieve_data\ntrigger: client submits query + limit\nwhy: request top-k internal evidence"] --> B["Service entry\nfile: src/backend/services/internal_data_service.py\nfunction: retrieve_internal_data(payload, db)\ndata: query text, limit\nwhy: compute semantic matches"]

    B --> C{"Branch by DB dialect\nfunction: retrieve_internal_data\ncondition: db.get_bind().dialect.name == 'postgresql'\ntradeoff: pgvector ranking vs deterministic local fallback"}

    C -->|"postgres"| D["DB-side ranking\nfunction: retrieve_internal_data\ndata: embedding cosine_distance ordering\nwhy: run nearest-neighbor ordering in Postgres"]
    C -->|"non-postgres"| E["In-process fallback ranking\nfunction: retrieve_internal_data\ndata: cosine_similarity(query_embedding, chunk.embedding)\nwhy: keep tests deterministic on SQLite"]

    D --> F["Map rows -> InternalRetrievedChunk\nfunction: retrieve_internal_data\ndata moved: chunk_id/document metadata/content/score/chunk_metadata\nwhy: stable API contract for callers"]
    E --> F

    G["Chunk write path\nfile: src/backend/services/internal_data_service.py\nfunction: _persist_documents\ndata: chunk_metadata={source, topic}\nwhy: preserve attribution at ingest time"] --> F

    F --> H["InternalDataRetrieveResponse\nfile: src/backend/schemas/internal_data.py\nfunction: InternalRetrievedChunk\noutput: includes chunk_metadata for source/topic attribution"]

    I["Downstream consumer\nfile: src/backend/services/retrieval_service.py\nfunction: execute_subquery_retrieval\nwhy: agent retrieval payload now carries attribution metadata"] --> H

